Package: BFCS
Title: Bayes Factors for Covariance Structures
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Ioan Gabriel",
           family = "Bucur",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "g.bucur@cs.ru.nl")
Description: This is an implementation of the BFCS algorithm, which is described
  in the article "A Bayesian Approach for Inferring Local Causal Structure in 
  Gene Regulatory Networks", published in Proceedings of Machine Learning 
  Research, Volume 72 (PGM 2018), and in the extension "Large-scale local causal 
  inference of gene regulatory relationships", published in the International
  Journal of Approximate Reasoning, Volume 115.
